44-4106.Preferred providers, defined.

Preferred providers shall mean providers of health services who agree to furnish services in a manner reasonably expected to contain or lower costs by contracting with insurers and participants in insurance arrangements or an insurer or participant organized as a provider of health services providing such services under a preferred provider contract.

SourceLaws 1984, LB 902, ยง 6.
